{"tid":1617633,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"買左保險可以換agent 嗎","createTime":"2019-10-04T00:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T06:54:22.000Z","uid":189395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e82aad259f90ff0177c0ce84957372e31090ec7d","tid":1617633,"uid":189395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:44:05.000Z","msg":"我大大話話都供左AIA 份保險成十年<br />\n中間有加過d 早排仲買左份年金<br />\n但係個agent 成日愛理不理咁 <br />\n我搬左都兩年 一早通知左轉地址 <br />\n前排唔見左張信用卡 cut 左就連自動轉帳都無左<br />\n我醒唔起交錢比人cut 左張單 原來封追數信仲寄去舊地址<br />\n搵個agent 做翻auto pat 仲叫我自己上網交<br />\n<br />\n勁想換個agent 有沒有巴絲好介紹"},{"pid":"b4bedb76d369e1a1a216e796ebe1e2395f8ccf9d","tid":1617633,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:44:26.000Z","msg":"#請廣傳 <br />\n<br />\n香港人俾政府恰到上心口！<br />\n「反蒙面法」有機會今日立埋<br />\n如果你連三罷公投都唔表態<br />\n你 註定輸一世！<br />\n<br />\n公投截止日期：10月11日中午12點<br />\n<br />\nThe Government treat all HongKongers as nothing and they also want to pass the anti-mask law to tackle protesters.<br />\nIt is time for us to speak up! Let&rsquo;s give your opinion on performing general strike.<br />\n<br />\nDeadline: 11 Oct 2019 1200 HKT<br />\n<br />\n公投傳送門：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=309e5585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a>"},{"pid":"a107d556616f2d11c49bdc95a55ffed84367ae17","tid":1617633,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T00:53:02.000Z","msg":"打去aia問"},{"pid":"25507b75f544f876f3067b126ac61664c5d206f5","tid":1617633,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T01:17:01.000Z","msg":"可以，試過<br />\n去AIA總部靜坐抗議同遞交請願信就得"},{"pid":"dba6ad26e466682794df903225b8bab8c5095a9c","tid":1617633,"uid":7353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:34:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9176577e9afd7c9bc9716a9be92